I tried to like Dune. The production design is fantastic and its universe is epic. But it kind of dragged. The pacing was bad, could hardly hear the dialogue above the obnoxiously loud score and the characters robotically boring.

Me, a freshman in high school: Wow, is there any book more boring than Dune?

Me, at 26: [fist pumping because the duchess just sassed someone at a dinner party] HOW CAN ONE BOOK BE THIS FUCKIN COOL???
